channel.title: I would love some help, cant get started D:
channel.description:
I played this a few years back and things have changed alot. i feel stupid for asking but i go to moparisthebest.com i find a server at the top i run it on high quality, i have a new windows 7 laptop. everything loads great i type in a user & pass. i sign in! but the screen stays black and says "loading-please wait"
how can i get around this? or what am i doing wrong?
thanks alot for suggestions & help.
